// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0578 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 2f869821-4c2f-5652-abba-aa7d86ea346c

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
